# Field — Styles

CSS file: `@acko/css/field.css`

## CSS Classes

- `.acko-field` — `@apply flex flex-col`, `gap: var(--scale-4)` (4px)
- `.acko-field-label` — typography: `font-label-lg` tokens; `color: var(--color-text-default)`
- `.acko-field-label-focused` — focused state: `color: var(--color-primary)`
- `.acko-field-label-disabled` — `color: var(--color-text-secondary)`
- `.acko-field-required` — `color: var(--color-error); margin-left: 2px`
- `.acko-field-helper` — `font-size: var(--font-caption-size); color: var(--color-text-secondary)`
- `.acko-field-error` — `font-size: var(--font-caption-size); color: var(--color-error-text)` (label does NOT turn red on error)
